    <h1>Crown_Damage_Ratio_FileFormat</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <p><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,112,192);"><strong>Crown =E2=80=93 C=
reate DR File for CRI Exposure Analysis</strong></span> <br class=3D"atl-fo=
rced-newline"> <strong>Objective</strong>: To create the damage ratio based=
 on Analysis Type =E2=80=93 Shape, Ring, and Custom Shape Analysis.<br> *1.=
 Shape Analysis =E2=80=93 DR file:-* <br> In case of shape Analysis job 1<s=
up>st</sup> and 2<sup>nd</sup> column in the excel sheet should always be "=
MinAttributeValue" and "MaxAttributeValue" whereas the last column should b=
e DR (damage ratio)<br> EX- </p>=20
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>=20
<tr>=20
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>MinAttributeValue</p></td>=20
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>MaxAttributeValue</p></td>=20
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>DR</p></td>=20
</tr>=20
<tr>=20
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>0</p></td>=20
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>40</p></td>=20
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>50</p></td>=20
</tr>=20
<tr>=20
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>40</p></td>=20
