<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>70</p></td>=20
</tr>=20
</tbody>
</table>
</div>=20
<p><br class=3D"atl-forced-newline"> *2. Custom Shape Analysis =E2=80=93 DR=
 file:-* <br> In case of custom shape Analysis 1<sup>st</sup> column in the=
 excel sheet should always be "ShapeName" whereas the last column should be=
 DR (damage ratio).<br> EX- </p>=20
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>=20
<tr>=20
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>ShapeName</p></td>=20
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>DR </p></td>=20
</tr>=20
<tr>=20
