</div>=20
<p><br class=3D"atl-forced-newline"> 3. Ring Analysis =E2=80=93 DR file:-<b=
r> In case of Ring Analysis 1<sup>st</sup> column in the excel sheet should=
 always be "Radius" whereas the last column should be DR (damage ratio)<br>=
 For Ring Analysis =E2=80=93 There are 4 type of Scale:- <br> 1. Feet<br> 2=
. Meter<br> 3. Kilometer<br> 4. Mile <br class=3D"atl-forced-newline"> <br =
class=3D"atl-forced-newline"> Ex of Feet Scale:- </p>=20
